{
  "stem": "1316.1",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So to Warsaw to the original police office.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And when the policeman took us and the guard to the train, outside my mother, my three sisters, and my little brother all were there.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And they met me with a big cry.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And but the policeman took us over to the station right away across.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "That took us to Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "We were in that place investigated, photographed, fingerprinted.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But then, after about two weeks, they called me in the office, and my father was there.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "He signed that he's a responsible.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "They freed us because we were too young, first-time offenders.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And on the way back, I promised my father not to go back to this organization.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I still was interested in this.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "But soon, I got disappointed because there were the-- the trials in Moscow.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And we heard about the shootings and the murder of all those old Bolsheviks and so on.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And we realized-- I soon realized, I and a few of my friends, that we were cheated.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "We [? are ?] [? served ?] [? a ?] [? false ?] [? god. ?] And we had a group going around, talking and discussing, until we organized this Bundist.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "We wanted to have a legal outlet.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "The bund was legal, a Social Jewish Democratic Party.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And we opened a youth-- a youth club there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "We had about 200 children, and we organized excursions and so on and opening.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And I was very busy with this, while at the same time I was working as an apprentice at the boot-stitching shop.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "My father gave it-- gave me in the [POLISH].",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And then the war broke out.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not at all.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yeah, we had-- in our restaurant, we had some customer Poles.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
